<h1>DRAFT - About - The Current Team and Management structureTO BE DELETED</h1>

<p>DRAFT - About - T&lt;p&gt;As with any large project the many activities being undertaken by a variety of volunteers requires an organisational structure to keep all work carefully focused on the objectives of FreeREG.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;			FreeReg Executive: Responsible to the FreeUKGen Society for the management of FreeREG : Eric Dickens (Chair), Mick Claxton (Data), Mark James (Training), John Pingram (Coordinators)&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;County coordinators: Liaise with FreeREG Executive, syndicate coordinators and web page editors to keep county pages up to date.	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Syndicate coordinators: Liaison with County coordinators, Data editors and transcribers to enter register data&amp;#160; &lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Transcribers: Volunteers who transcribe registers and submit data to the County coordinators or to the Data Editors.&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Document (Web Pages) coordinator: Oversees general structure and presentation of web pages and liaison with the web page editors.&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Web Page Editors: 	Maintains a group of specific webpages such as the County Pages, FAQ pages, etc. 	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Discussion Forum and Mailing List Administrators: Moderates discussion fora and managing mailing lists,dealing with problem subscribe and unsubscribe messages, handling error messages and rejected messages.&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Database Coordinator: Overseeing the database aspect of the project.&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Data Manager: Overseeing final data entry into the database.&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Database Developers: Maintain the website and work on enhancements.&lt;/p&gt;<br />&lt;p&gt;Data Editors: Convert data from non-standard format into our format as csv files. &lt;br /&gt;		&lt;/p&gt;</p>